block content
    p Hi #{firstName},
    p Welcome to **Toundify**—where meaningful conversations come to life 🎉🙏!
    p We’re excited to have you join our community of chat enthusiasts. Whether you're here to stay connected with friends, collaborate with colleagues, or explore new connections, Toundify Chat is designed to make every interaction seamless, secure, and enjoyable.
    table.btn.btn-primary(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
        tbody
            tr
                td(align='left')
                    table(role='presentation', border='0', cellpadding='0', cellspacing='0')
                        tbody
                            tr
                                td
                                    a(href=`${url}`, target='_blank') Start Now!
